Poor Spikey.
Can't be a human,
can't be a vampire.

39:44.615 --> 39:46.585
Where the hell
do you fit in?

39:52.322 --> 39:54.259
Your job is
to kill the Slayer,

39:54.291 --> 39:57.262
but all you can do is
follow me around
making moon eyes.

39:57.295 --> 40:00.532
-I'm in love with you.
-You're in love with pain.

40:00.565 --> 40:03.268
Admit it. You like me

40:03.300 --> 40:05.603
because you enjoy
getting beat down.

40:05.637 --> 40:09.440
So really,
who's screwed up?
Hello. Vampire.

40:11.009 --> 40:13.411
I'm supposed to be
treading on the dark side.

40:22.119 --> 40:24.289
What's your excuse?

40:32.664 --> 40:35.132
* I can't find the time
and place *

40:35.166 --> 40:37.902
* To say what
I need to sa-a-ay *

40:37.936 --> 40:40.005
* I just wanna run away

40:40.038 --> 40:42.039
So we've kind of
played this scene.

40:43.273 --> 40:46.311
Yeah.
Return.

40:46.344 --> 40:51.617
* What is wrong with you?

40:51.650 --> 40:54.018
* What is wrong here?

40:54.052 --> 40:59.891
I-- I just keep thinking
there's gotta be someplace,
like, bigger than this.

41:01.659 --> 41:04.630
Besides, it's way too early
to go home yet.

41:11.168 --> 41:13.605
I wasn't planning
on hurting you... much.

41:13.639 --> 41:15.806
You haven't even come
close to hurting me.

41:15.840 --> 41:17.141
Afraid to give me
the chance?

41:22.648 --> 41:24.181
You afraid I'm gonna--

41:49.740 --> 41:51.543
(zipper unzipping)

42:01.418 --> 42:04.856
(grunting)

42:13.965 --> 42:16.568
(inaudible)

43:11.356 --> 43:13.759
Grr! Arrgh!
